General.Name: Kaufman Et Broad
General.Description: Kaufman & Broad S.A. operates as a property developer and builder in France. It designs, develops, builds, and sells single-family homes in communities, managed residences, offices, shops, hotels, and logistics platforms and business parks. The company was founded in 1968 and is headquartered in Courbevoie, France.
